name: DICE OGRE
description:
This DICE OGRE was summoned through an archaic ritual devised by the worshipers of the GOMAVERSE.

Though tall in stature and intimidating in appearance, this ogre is quite harmless and friendly. 

Their hobbies include: gambling, gambling, gambling, gambling, gambling, gambling, gambling, gambling, gambling, gambling, hot sauce and gambling.
